features: ❤【Large Capacity】9 drawer fabric storage dresser is designed to satisfy various storage needs. The wood top is great for keeping the most-used items within your reach. With plentiful space to organize all your belongings, your room will always be kept in perfect order. Overall Dimensions: 34.45" L x 12.6" W x 41.34" H. Drawer Dimensions: 10.63" L x 11.42" W x 8.66" H.

❤【Room for Expansion】Having a Closet of drawers with a large capacity allows you to accommodate future additions to your wardrobe without worrying about running out of storage space. This is especially useful if you tend to acquire new clothing or frequently rotate your seasonal wardrobe.

❤【Sturdy Structure】Sufulaa 9-drawer storage dresser is equipped with a sturdy steel frame and high-quality wooden top, besides, this rustic wooden bedroom dresser is combined with MDF board and non-woven fabric, which provides excellent stability and durability, ensuring that the wide dresser can withstand regular use and support the weight of your clothing and belongings.

❤【Multifunctional Application】This 4-tier fabric storage dresser for bedroom accommodates potted plants, photo albums, books, makeup mirrors, desk lamps and tea sets. It’s suitable for wherever you want to keep clutter under control, such as bedrooms, dressing rooms, entryways.

❤【Easy Assemble】The package includes clear assemble instructions and numbered parts, which makes it convenient to set up the bins.
